<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">On the other hand, the general idea of =E2=80=
=9Ceverything is securities fraud=E2=80=9D is that if investors care about =
a thing, and the company says misleading stuff about the thing, then that=
=E2=80=99s securities fraud.=C2=A0<em>Traditionally</em>, investors cared a=
bout things like profits, and companies sometimes cooked their books to sho=
