<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The way corporate earnings generally work is t=
hat a company puts out a press release with all of its material financial r=
esults for the quarter, and then it usually has a public conference call in=
 which it answers questions about those numbers. =E2=80=9CCould you explain=
