<div id=3D"footnote-7" class=3D"footnote-content" style=3D"font-style: ital=
ic;">
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">[7] Actually there is a complication there: So=
me contracts obviously can give outsiders control over a company=E2=80=99s =
